# CRM v5 Rules

- Use server components by default for Supabase queries.
- All forms must use Zod schemas with shadcn/ui Form components.
- Follow existing entity patterns in /lib/entities or /app/(crm)/...
- Prefer Biome formatting; never use ESLint/Prettier.
- Keep components small and composable.